&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a Senior Account Executive to drive business development for our services and equipment business. This is a high-impact, high-visibility role that reports directly to the CEO. This role is ideal for someone who thrives at the intersection of science and sales and wants to help shape the commercial future of a biotech company.&lt;/p&gt;
